### Health check
GET https://localhost:8443/api/users/health HTTP/1.1

### Login
POST https://localhost:8443/api/users/auth/login HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "username": "bruno",
    "password": "bruno123"
}

###
POST https://localhost:8443/api/users/auth/login HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "username": "maurodri",
    "password": "maurodri123"
}

###
POST https://localhost:8443/api/users/auth/login HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "username": "bira",
    "password": "bira123"
}

###
POST https://localhost:8443/api/users/auth/login HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "admin"
}

### Refresh (replace <refresh_token> with the refresh_token from login response)
POST https://localhost:8443/api/users/auth/refresh HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "refresh_token": "<refresh_token>"
}

### Me (replace <access_token> with the access_token from login response)
GET https://localhost:8443/api/users/auth/me HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>

### Register
POST https://localhost:8443/api/users/auth/register HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "username": "maurodri",
    "password": "maurodri123"
}
